title: KD & AD Injured, Phoenix Suns, Nets-Lakers, Fan Questions | WHAT’S BURNIN’
itunes:title: KD & AD Injured, Phoenix Suns, Nets-Lakers, Fan Questions | WHAT’S BURNIN’
description:
Matt and Stak return for another episode of Whats Burnin'. The boys discuss the latest injury news for Kevin Durant and Anthony Davis, discuss the Suns hot stretch, and the Hawks cold streak. Plus, they preview a big week ahead including the Nets and Jazz both taking on the Lakers & Clippers. Also, the guys answer your fan questions and discuss trade targets around the league.
